item.title: CVE-2021-38324|2024-08-04T01:37:16.332Z -- sp%20rental%20manager -- sp%20rental%20manager
item.description: The SP Rental Manager WordPress plugin is vulnerable to SQL Injection via the orderby parameter found in the ~/user/shortcodes.php file which allows attackers to retrieve information contained in a site's database, in versions up to and including 1.5.3.
